      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really nice shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid car without the brand-new price tag. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did! Feel free to ask me any questions!",
