    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure mechanical longevity. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack, while the suspension bushings remain compliant for precision cornering. Showing honest signs of use consistent with its status, this M3 is mechanically tight and represents a pure, analog performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
